'''{{lang|pl|Jerzy Samuel Bandtkie}}''' (also spelled '''Bandtke'''; 1768–1835) was a Polish linguist, [[Philology|philologist]], historian, [[bibliographer]] and [[Lexicography|lexicographer]].

